{"tid":2037053,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[0527] 我好想返工 你廢青千祈唔好咁做阻我返工","createTime":"2020-05-26T21:44:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T00:43:48.000Z","uid":168391,"like":7,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6cfc89b8fe850fb50de118ca923119c03e286114","tid":2037053,"uid":168391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T21:44:30.000Z","msg":"前排減緊肥，每朝都<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">白粥加蘿蔔汁</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有次趕時間出門口，含住啲白粥同蘿蔔汁就衝左落樓下搭鐵，你知啦，我唔可以遲到㗎嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知咁急住食覺得好難頂，唔太吞得落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去到鐵入面，好撚多人，比人撞一撞，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我都未吞得切就噴哂啲粥落地下</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n周圍啲人即刻彈開，我係咁話我唔係嘔，佢地都唔聽，搞到我好尷尬下站落車轉巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">後尾聽講話原來有人嘔，地鐵要原廠返去消毒！</span></strong></span><br />\n好彩我落左車如果唔係都返唔切工！<br />\n<br />\n你班友<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">千祈唔好</span></strong></span>做啲咁核突既野扮嘔塞鐵呀，我真係好想返工㗎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b9f0185b51dcfb474bd30ad76827ff0b66eb08","tid":2037053,"uid":168391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T21:44:51.000Z","msg":"我好想翻工<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd5d2e217b07d9991f2d296c82c24f57e6c94f0c","tid":2037053,"uid":168391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T21:45:15.000Z","msg":"俾我翻工呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2b21c8bb863477397fba5c02d8d117001ae9d5a","tid":2037053,"uid":168391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T21:45:41.000Z","msg":"呀叔我要搵錢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66876df85284ff347bda079f65a64800fbb414de","tid":2037053,"uid":168391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T21:46:16.000Z","msg":"大家早晨 我又要返工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe02b2da6b93b90e5ca95c78b721a8e08c127da","tid":2037053,"uid":168391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T21:46:39.000Z","msg":"早晨<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a47aa44f7ac421cebe8ba755366eba7c032c2815","tid":2037053,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T21:48:12.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"8e0066bae816acb61c480d210542e056c2ec9b2f","tid":2037053,"uid":39245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T21:49:49.000Z","msg":"琴晚早講丫嗎屌，咁早點搵粥同robert，煲都煲唔切啦"},{"pid":"e3007738f7cedfef58628272e6c70c0ebf22b037","tid":2037053,"uid":285831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T21:50:00.000Z","msg":"我都想返工呀！已經起左身準備返工！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" cl